    "causal_summary": "Once Phase 0 (`001-foundation`) ships its measurement plane, the 013 research identified six concrete JS-only capability opportunities the styles database does not yet have: DOM-derived layout fingerprints, screenshot-based palette/dedupe, a shadow multimodal retrieval lane, batched embeddings, an auto-reindex watcher, and (conditionally) a parsed-projection cache",
